data.description: Move-in ready 4 Bedroom, 2.5 Bath Home in sought-after Bethlehem without the restrictions of an HOA. This meticulously maintained Home is situated on a corner lot and offers numerous upgrades over new construction, including upgraded flooring throughout the main level, an advanced security system, an integrated UV air purifier, a premium appliance package, and more. The Foyer welcomes you inside, provides access to a Powder Room, and opens to a separate room perfect for a Formal Living Room or Home Office. Continue inside to the open floor plan providing a spacious Chef's Kitchen with a large island, perfect for entertaining and meal prep, granite countertops, a walk-in Pantry, and premium stainless-steel appliances. Upstairs, retreat to the stunning Primary Suite, including a tray ceiling and a luxurious ensuite with dual vanities, a large shower, a separate garden tub, and an expansive walk-in closet. The second level also provides three additional Guest Bedrooms, a Guest Bathroom, and a Laundry Room with space for extra storage. This Home is truly turnkey, as the price includes furnishings, a comprehensive 1 year 2-10 Home Warranty, and the remaining Structure Home Warranty through 2030. Potential to take advantage of an assumable loan at an amazing 2.375% APR. Applicants must qualify; terms and conditions apply.
